    <text id="d1">
        <body id="d2">
        	<div1 type="letter" id="d3">
        		<pb entity="DSSR_000002759_0027"/>
        		<head>Monroe Thayer to Friend Guardden <date value="1862-06-17">June 17 1862 </date></head>
        		
        		<opener>
            <dateline>
            <date value="1862-06-17">June 17 1862</date> 10 Regt mass Vol<lb/>
            Monroe Thayer Co. C
            </dateline>
            <salute>My kind Friend Guardden</salute>
        		</opener>
        		
        		<p>
            I hope you ar Well and<lb/>
            all your Family.  there<lb/>
            is no Postage stamp Down here<lb/>
            and I <add place="top" hand="author">Wish</add> you Would Send Some<lb/>
            to me and you Will See<lb/>
            A bout 20 Dolars Gowing<lb/>
            up to you one of these<lb/>
            Dayes I Supose you ar<lb/>
            Discureged But you must<lb/>
            not Be you must Writ<lb/>
            Mee alletter I am home<lb/>
            Sick and you must Write<lb/>
            mee a letter and you must<lb/> 
            Let mee know A Bout farm<lb/>
            tell meee How Dick and<lb/>
            Charley is and you must<lb/>
            tell William how had<lb/>
            ought to thank his
            
            <pb entity="DSSR_000002759_0028" n="[page 2]"/>
        			
            Father for not leting<lb/>
            him go to War and <unclear>[word lined out]</unclear> <add place="bottom" hand="author">now</add> <lb/>
            I Wish my Self that I<lb/>
            had not Inlisted my<lb/>
            Self but now I <del hand="author" rend="line-through">me</del> ame<lb/>
            here and must Stay<lb/>
            till it is over.  I now<lb/>
            Will tell you how to<lb/>
            Diricet A letter to mee<lb/>
            and you must Send<lb/>
            nice one now I Will<lb/>
            tell you.  Gen Keyes Corps.<lb/>
            D. Armey.. Gen.. Cough <unclear>[word lined out]</unclear><lb/>
            Division.. Gen.. Devens<lb/>
            Brigade..<lb/>
            Monroe Thayer Co C<lb/>
            10 Regt.   mass Vol.<lb/>
        		</p>
        		
        		<closer>
        		<salute>Good By</salute>
            </closer>
        		
        		<pb entity="DSSR_000002759_0029"/>
        		<pb entity="DSSR_000002759_0030"/>
        		
        		</div1>
        </body>
    </text>
